body_html:
CSV should be working fine in the current release, as should JSON.

@CJxD, thanks for sharing that workaround! Like @dandelionmane said, this isn't really high-priority for us at this time, so I'm closing it for now. If you like, feel free to open an issue in our new repository at https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorboard/issues. Thanks!
